# Tachibana Agent Skill

## Connection

- **Server:** `{{{server_origin}}}`
- **Authorization:** `Bearer {{{auth_token}}}`

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/health` | Health check |
| GET | `/api/devices` | List connected devices |
| GET | `/api/devices/:udid` | Get device info |
| GET | `/api/devices/:udid/apps` | List installed apps |
| GET | `/api/devices/:udid/photos` | List photos |
| GET | `/api/devices/:udid/photos/:id` | Get photo |

## Authentication

Include the following header in all requests:

```
Authorization: Bearer {{{auth_token}}}
```
